about.summary: Generates Python Extension modules from commented Cython CXD files

name: autowrap
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "autowrap" %}
{% set version = "0.15.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "3ec93792773c5d7250ea6a43a861cb070350e723be78273dc98d5fbeb480af95" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt
  entry_points:
    - autowrap = autowrap.Main:main

requirements:
  build:
    - toolchain
    - python
    - setuptools
    - cython ==0.21
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - cython ==0.21

test:
  imports:
    - autowrap
    - autowrap.data_files
  commands:
    - autowrap --version

about:
  home: https://github.com/uweschmitt/autowrap
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  # autowrap does not include its license file in the latest pypi release,
  # but will in the next release.  (TODO for next release)
  summary: 'Generates Python Extension modules from commented Cython CXD files'
  dev_url: https://github.com/uweschmitt/autowrap

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - aseyboldt

about.summary: Generates Python Extension modules from commented Cython CXD files
